The following code gives the compiler error "Unresolved reference: INFO" for both lines:

 import org.apache.log4j.Level
 
 fun main(args : Array<String>) {
    val level1 = Level.INFO
    val level2 : org.apache.log4j.Level = org.apache.log4j.Level.INFO
 }

Confirmed as bug in http://devnet.jetbrains.net/message/5458486#5458486